original: Laurell, Frans Emanuel (Manne), tandläkare, Linköping, f. 23/9/91 i Linköp. G. 25 m. Anne-Louise Wahr-gren. Barn r Ann-Cathrine f. 29, Ann-Margret 31, Lilleman 39, Madelaine 45. — Studrex. i Örebro 10, tandlrkand. 12, tandlrex. 14. Anst. v. byggn rverk-samh. i Sthlm 30-32, i Linköp. o. Strängnäs 39-43, praktik i Smedjebacken o. Västerås, i Linköp. sed. 43. Hobby r konst.
translated: Laurell, Frans Emanuel (Manne), dentist, Linköping, b. 23/9/91 in Linköping. Married in 1925 to Anne-Louise Wahr-gren. They have children: Ann-Cathrine b. 1929, Ann-Margret b. 1931, Lilleman b. 1939, Madelaine b. 1945. - Studied in Örebro until 1910, dentistry studies until 1912, specialized studies until 1914. Employed by construction company in Stockholm from 1930-1932, in Linköping and Strängnäs from 1939-1943, practiced in Smedjebacken and Västerås, in Linköping since 1943. Hobby is art.
